.IP "\fBsei\fR" 4
.IX Item "sei"
Set \s-1SEI\s0 message types to include.
Some combination of the following values:
.RS 4
.IP "\fBhdr\fR" 4
.IX Item "hdr"
Include \s-1HDR\s0 metadata if the input frames have it
(\fImastering_display_colour_volume\fR and \fIcontent_light_level\fR
