The previous output \s-1DTS.\s0
.IP "\fB\s-1PREV_OUTPTS\s0\fR" 4
.IX Item "PREV_OUTPTS"
The previous output \s-1PTS.\s0
.IP "\fB\s-1TB\s0\fR" 4
.IX Item "TB"
The timebase of stream packet belongs.
.IP "\fB\s-1SR\s0\fR" 4
.IX Item "SR"
The sample rate of stream packet belongs.
