.Sp
To map all video (or audio) streams to an AdaptationSet, \*(L"v\*(R" (or \*(L"a\*(R") can be used as stream identifier instead of IDs.
.Sp
When no assignment is defined, this defaults to an AdaptationSet for each stream.
.Sp
