\&        \-map \*(Aq[FL]\*(Aq front_left.wav \-map \*(Aq[FR]\*(Aq front_right.wav \-map \*(Aq[FC]\*(Aq
\&        front_center.wav \-map \*(Aq[LFE]\*(Aq lfe.wav \-map \*(Aq[SL]\*(Aq side_left.wav \-map \*(Aq[SR]\*(Aq
\&        side_right.wav
