Perform \s-1HDR\s0(High Dynamic Range) to \s-1SDR\s0(Standard Dynamic Range) conversion with tone-mapping.
It maps the dynamic range of \s-1HDR10\s0 content to the \s-1SDR\s0 content.
It currently only accepts \s-1HDR10\s0 as input.
.PP
It accepts the following parameters:
.IP "\fBformat\fR" 4
.IX Item "format"
Specify the output pixel format.
.Sp
Currently supported formats are:
.RS 4
.IP "\fIp010\fR" 4
.IX Item "p010"
.PD 0
.IP "\fInv12\fR" 4
.IX Item "nv12"
.RE
.RS 4
.PD
.Sp
Default is nv12.
.RE
