.IX Item "rf"
.PD 0
.IP "\fBgf\fR" 4
.IX Item "gf"
.IP "\fBbf\fR" 4
.IX Item "bf"
.IP "\fBaf\fR" 4
.IX Item "af"
.PD
Specify the red, green, blue and alpha fade. Default values are \f(CW15\fR,
\&\f(CW10\fR, \f(CW5\fR and \f(CW5\fR.
Allowed range is \f(CW\*(C`[0, 255]\*(C'\fR.
.IP "\fBzoom\fR" 4
.IX Item "zoom"
Set the zoom factor. Default value is \f(CW1\fR. Allowed range is \f(CW\*(C`[0, 10]\*(C'\fR.
Values lower than \fI1\fR will auto adjust zoom factor to maximal possible value.
.IP "\fBdraw\fR" 4
.IX Item "draw"
Set the vectorscope drawing mode.
